  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 11.78,
      "text": "임여사시 조정현의 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.78,
      "end": 16.93,
      "text": "해봐요 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.93,
      "end": 25.52,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.52,
      "end": 59.97,
      "text": "영어가 즐거워지는 영어 놀이터"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.97,
      "end": 61.43,
      "text": "Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.43,
      "end": 63.77,
      "text": "6월엔 베르히만 아일랜드"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.77,
      "end": 68.57,
      "text": "A film-making couple, Chris and Tony Sanders traveled to Pharaoh"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.57,
      "end": 73.69,
      "text": "The island where Ingmar Bergman lived and worked to attend a film screening"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.69,
      "end": 77.21,
      "text": "Oh, 너무 멋지게 이름도 소개해주셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.85,
      "end": 80.37,
      "text": "Chris도 나오고, Tony도 나오고"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.37,
      "end": 83.99,
      "text": "근데 이 부부가 Travel to Pharaoh"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.99,
      "end": 84.79,
      "text": "이거 되게 어려웠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.81,
      "end": 86.09,
      "text": "그죠, 이거 스웨디쉬라서"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.09,
      "end": 87.49,
      "text": "F-A-R-O, 스웨디쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.49,
      "end": 91.41,
      "text": "And in the Swedish language, they write letters very differently."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.65,
      "end": 91.93,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.99,
      "end": 93.75,
      "text": "They put little dots and lines"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.75,
      "end": 95.59,
      "text": "It's almost like 한글"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.59,
      "end": 96.95,
      "text": "플러스 알파벳"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.95,
      "end": 97.91,
      "text": "합친 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.91,
      "end": 99.11,
      "text": "이거 뭘까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.45,
      "end": 100.45,
      "text": "무식한 미국인"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.45,
      "end": 101.93,
      "text": "이해하기 힘들어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.97,
      "end": 103.39,
      "text": "아이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.39,
      "end": 105.69,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 영화를 통해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.69,
      "end": 106.23,
      "text": "이"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.23,
      "end": 107.83,
      "text": "Pharo 라고 읽어야 되는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.83,
      "end": 109.63,
      "text": "Phoree 라고 읽어야 되는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.63,
      "end": 111.09,
      "text": "함께 들으면 되는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.29,
      "end": 111.41,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.55,
      "end": 112.59,
      "text": "그 G 안에 들어가면"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.59,
      "end": 113.71,
      "text": "Fargo"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.71,
      "end": 115.01,
      "text": "A famous movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.01,
      "end": 116.69,
      "text": "반가운 영화 나오는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.69,
      "end": 117.61,
      "text": "Fargo"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.61,
      "end": 118.63,
      "text": "Very funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.63,
      "end": 119.65,
      "text": "Very dark"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.65,
      "end": 120.49,
      "text": "Anyway"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.49,
      "end": 121.97,
      "text": "미국인 입장이고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.09,
      "end": 122.45,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.45,
      "end": 123.91,
      "text": "자, 이 커플이요"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.91,
      "end": 125.93,
      "text": "이 작품을 만들기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.93,
      "end": 127.43,
      "text": "이곳을 온 것이 아니었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.65,
      "end": 129.03,
      "text": "작품도 만들면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.03,
      "end": 129.47,
      "text": "동시에"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.47,
      "end": 130.79,
      "text": "To attend a film screening"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.79,
      "end": 131.59,
      "text": "감사, 감사"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.59,
      "end": 133.81,
      "text": "I'll kill him two birds with one stone"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.81,
      "end": 134.97,
      "text": "그렇죠, 딱이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.15,
      "end": 137.45,
      "text": "특히 남편 Tony's film screening"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.45,
      "end": 139.13,
      "text": "He was held on this island"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.13,
      "end": 139.79,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.79,
      "end": 141.61,
      "text": "And this is a special island"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.61,
      "end": 142.97,
      "text": "Because it's where"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.97,
      "end": 145.33,
      "text": "Ingmar Bergman lived and worked"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.33,
      "end": 145.97,
      "text": "That's meaningful"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.97,
      "end": 148.21,
      "text": "It was his favorite place to visit"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.21,
      "end": 149.37,
      "text": "Yeah, 그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.37,
      "end": 151.43,
      "text": "그의 영화를 감상을 한"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.43,
      "end": 152.93,
      "text": "많은 오리언스가 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.93,
      "end": 154.77,
      "text": "He's got good reviews from them"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.77,
      "end": 157.11,
      "text": "아주 칭찬 일색이더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.11,
      "end": 158.45,
      "text": "He has a lot of fans"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.45,
      "end": 158.73,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.73,
      "end": 159.45,
      "text": "They like him"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.45,
      "end": 162.21,
      "text": "I think he has a big ego"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.21,
      "end": 164.57,
      "text": "Because many people"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.57,
      "end": 165.81,
      "text": "are praising him"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.81,
      "end": 168.01,
      "text": "And his wife feels a little lonely"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.01,
      "end": 170.41,
      "text": "So I see the kind of tension"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.41,
      "end": 171.13,
      "text": "between them"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.13,
      "end": 172.85,
      "text": "But it's beautiful"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.85,
      "end": 174.49,
      "text": "because they're a 부부"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.49,
      "end": 175.15,
      "text": "부부니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.15,
      "end": 176.49,
      "text": "상호 보완하면 되니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.49,
      "end": 176.93,
      "text": "그러니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.93,
      "end": 178.47,
      "text": "남편이 잘되면"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.47,
      "end": 179.69,
      "text": "그래도 응원하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.69,
      "end": 180.89,
      "text": "자기도 좋을 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.89,
      "end": 181.29,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.29,
      "end": 181.63,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.63,
      "end": 183.03,
      "text": "자기 배우자 잘되는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.03,
      "end": 185.05,
      "text": "모든 사람들의 로망이 아닐까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.19,
      "end": 186.27,
      "text": "전반의 로망인가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.43,
      "end": 188.59,
      "text": "Not for you, 조세음?"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.67,
      "end": 190.23,
      "text": "아니, 저도 마찬가지예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.23,
      "end": 192.07,
      "text": "아, 웃음이 왜 터지는 거야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.77,
      "end": 193.41,
      "text": "뭐, 웃으세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.41,
      "end": 194.63,
      "text": "웃으면 보기 좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.63,
      "end": 196.69,
      "text": "윤인희님께서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.69,
      "end": 197.97,
      "text": "크쌤의 유쾌함에"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.97,
      "end": 199.53,
      "text": "하루 시작이 밝아지네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.53,
      "end": 200.29,
      "text": "하셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.29,
      "end": 201.23,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.23,
      "end": 203.01,
      "text": "제 말이 딱이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.01,
      "end": 204.23,
      "text": "Tell me about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.23,
      "end": 205.11,
      "text": "Tell you about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.11,
      "end": 207.07,
      "text": "I'll tell you some more about it"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.07,
      "end": 209.31,
      "text": "자, 이 배경지가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.31,
      "end": 210.29,
      "text": "전반적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.29,
      "end": 213.57,
      "text": "It wasn't a brightly sunny place"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.57,
      "end": 215.45,
      "text": "라고는 저는 묘사하고 싶지는 않아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.45,
      "end": 216.39,
      "text": "It was a little cloudy"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.39,
      "end": 218.01,
      "text": "그치만"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.01,
      "end": 219.07,
      "text": "Very calm"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.07,
      "end": 219.89,
      "text": "그리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.89,
      "end": 221.45,
      "text": "Beautiful하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.45,
      "end": 222.69,
      "text": "Peaceful하다는 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.69,
      "end": 224.07,
      "text": "전적으로 동감합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.07,
      "end": 224.87,
      "text": "Very peaceful"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.87,
      "end": 226.71,
      "text": "If you like to get away from people"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.71,
      "end": 228.21,
      "text": "For a quiet"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.21,
      "end": 229.23,
      "text": "Just get away"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.23,
      "end": 230.95,
      "text": "It's a perfect place now"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.95,
      "end": 232.03,
      "text": "This is the place"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.03,
      "end": 232.77,
      "text": "So 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.77,
      "end": 233.45,
      "text": "Feels like"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.45,
      "end": 235.01,
      "text": "I got some fresh air"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.01,
      "end": 235.55,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.55,
      "end": 237.39,
      "text": "영화를 보는 것만으로도"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.39,
      "end": 240.13,
      "text": "뭔가 신선한 공기를 들여 마시는 느낌이 들었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.13,
      "end": 241.57,
      "text": "Fresh sea air"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.57,
      "end": 243.31,
      "text": "And Faro"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.31,
      "end": 244.33,
      "text": "F-A-R-O"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.33,
      "end": 246.45,
      "text": "Is an island in the Baltic Sea"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.45,
      "end": 248.89,
      "text": "And it's part of Sweden"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.89,
      "end": 250.89,
      "text": "It's Sweden's largest island"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.89,
      "end": 253.17,
      "text": "North east of Gotland"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.17,
      "end": 255.11,
      "text": "So if you take a free ferry"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.11,
      "end": 257.15,
      "text": "Apparently they have a free ferry"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.15,
      "end": 258.85,
      "text": "A free boat from Gotland"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.85,
      "end": 260.05,
      "text": "To this island"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.05,
      "end": 261.31,
      "text": "If you'd like to visit"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.31,
      "end": 263.89,
      "text": "And it's well known for tourism"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.89,
      "end": 266.25,
      "text": "Because of this movie director"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.25,
      "end": 267.57,
      "text": "They have a whole center"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.57,
      "end": 268.29,
      "text": "Bergman Center"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.29,
      "end": 270.03,
      "text": "That's in honor of this director"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.03,
      "end": 270.51,
      "text": "Amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.51,
      "end": 271.47,
      "text": "And they have a tour"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.47,
      "end": 272.41,
      "text": "Where you can visit"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.41,
      "end": 273.67,
      "text": "All the movie sites"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.67,
      "end": 275.01,
      "text": "Where they shot scenes"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.01,
      "end": 275.87,
      "text": "For his movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.87,
      "end": 276.43,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.43,
      "end": 278.35,
      "text": "이 베르 이만 감독이라는 분이"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.35,
      "end": 280.19,
      "text": "Actually lived in that island"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.19,
      "end": 280.85,
      "text": "했기 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.85,
      "end": 282.55,
      "text": "많은 사람들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.55,
      "end": 284.39,
      "text": "Seem to be so proud of"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.39,
      "end": 285.33,
      "text": "The director"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.33,
      "end": 286.39,
      "text": "Yeah, he lived there"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.39,
      "end": 287.85,
      "text": "For over 40 years"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.85,
      "end": 288.27,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.27,
      "end": 290.57,
      "text": "Wow, that's why they have a safari"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.57,
      "end": 291.25,
      "text": "그러게"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.25,
      "end": 291.85,
      "text": "In this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.85,
      "end": 292.41,
      "text": "There's a safari"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.41,
      "end": 293.35,
      "text": "They actually have"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.35,
      "end": 294.67,
      "text": "A Bergman safari"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.67,
      "end": 295.51,
      "text": "저는 safari"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.51,
      "end": 296.35,
      "text": "라고 하면은"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.35,
      "end": 296.73,
      "text": "막"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.73,
      "end": 297.97,
      "text": "Giraffe 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.97,
      "end": 298.99,
      "text": "Yeah, elephant"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.99,
      "end": 299.81,
      "text": "Elephant 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.81,
      "end": 300.31,
      "text": "Hippos"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.31,
      "end": 301.33,
      "text": "I love hippos"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.33,
      "end": 302.23,
      "text": "그럴 줄 알았는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.23,
      "end": 304.23,
      "text": "아닌 상황이던데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.23,
      "end": 305.15,
      "text": "좀 실망했죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.15,
      "end": 306.93,
      "text": "I wanted to see the animals"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.93,
      "end": 309.51,
      "text": "But many movie buffs"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.51,
      "end": 311.41,
      "text": "This director has a lot of buffs"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.41,
      "end": 313.41,
      "text": "이 감독의 덕후들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.41,
      "end": 314.51,
      "text": "정말 많아서"
